OL,3,CScottish Borders Council to sell
OL,4,Cformer public toilets
OL,6,Fis offering a unique opportunity for
OL,7,Fpeople to purchase public toilets that
OL,8,Fare being sold.
OL,10,FThe council is looking for people who
OL,11,Fare interested from community groups
OL,12,Ffor the acquisition of the public
OL,13,Ftoilets that were permanently closed
OL,14,Fon March 2023.
OL,16,FThe facilities in s, Hawick and are
OL,17,Fdue to be sold off for what the
OL,18,Fcouncil says is "rationalisation" of
OL,19,Fpublic toilets in the Scottish Borders.
